    "description": "Manufactured OpenAPI artifact for Salt Edge API. This file was synthesized by Last Mile from curated research JSON and is not vendor-certified. Use it as an agent-consumable starting point, then validate paths, schemas, authentication, and server URLs with the vendor before production use. Salt Edge's public v6 documentation describes its Open Banking Gateway across Account Information, Payment Initiation, and Data Enrichment services, and the docs host publishes a downloadable Swagger JSON artifact. The public quick-start guides and reference material cover customer creation, connection initiation, account and transaction retrieval, provider and payment template selection, payment initiation, callback handling, request signing, widget flows, provider keys, dynamic registration, and enrichment services such as transaction categorization, merchant identification, and financial insights. This is a strong write-capable open-banking platform, but it does not represent asset or telemetry data. Asset data is Unsupported. Telemetry data is Unsupported. Writeback is Supported.",
